# ── Build output ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/bin/
**/obj/

# ── Visual Studio ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.rsuser
*.userosscache

# ── NuGet ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/packages/
**/project.nuget.cache
**/project.assets.json

# ── Addin manifest files (personal — each user generates their own from .addin.template) ──
*.addin

# ── Legacy single-file seeds + exported personal presets ──────────────────────
**/Checkup_Catalogs.json
**/Checkup_Capabilities.json
**/Checkup_Capabilities.json.migrated
Exported_*_Presets.json
# NOTE: Checkup_Settings.json IS tracked — it is the generic factory seed
# (StylePurge defaults + demo presets). Live user presets are stored in the
# Windows Registry, not in this file, so it carries no personal data.

# ── Test / sample data with company-specific content ──────────────────────────
**/Resources/Test_Spezifik.*

# ── Dotfuscator (config and output — not for public repo) ─────────────────────
**/Dotfuscator/

# ── Claude Code files (internal development tooling — not for public repo) ─────
**/.claude/
CLAUDE.md

# ── Local dev tooling (personal absolute paths inside — not for public repo) ───
/tools/
